Ton Book of Meme is a project restructured and developed by the Ton Genesis fund from its original project. Importantly, this project will be entirely community-driven. Utilizing the memecoin $BOME on Solana, Arweave, and IPFS as the primary storage for Ton Book of Meme, along with future expansions to Bitcoin inscriptions as immutable forever storage, this initiative aims to foster a new dimension of decentralized social media and make memes unstoppable on the Ton Bome platform. The project's direction will be determined solely by the community.
